OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777061156
OL,3,CChemo nurse takes campaign to lower
OL,4,Cbreast cancer screening age to
OL,5,CWestminster
OL,7,FA chemotherapy nurse from Thanet in
OL,8,FKent has taken her campaign to lower
OL,9,Fthe age women are invited for breast
OL,10,Fcancer screening - to Westminster.
OL,12,FGemma Reeves was joined by dozens of
OL,13,Fother women after more than 100,000
OL,14,Fpeople signed her petition to lower
OL,15,Fthe routine age for mammogram
OL,16,Fscreening to 40.
OL,18,FCurrently only those over the age of
OL,19,F50 are eligible.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
