OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777061156
OL,3,CChemo nurse takes campaign to lower
OL,4,Cbreast cancer screening age to
OL,5,CWestminster
OL,7,FThe petition also calls for those
OL,8,Falready being screened, to have
OL,9,Fscreening performed annually as
OL,10,Fopposed to every three years.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian chemotherapy
OL,13,Fnurse Gemma Reeves said: "The current
OL,14,Fbreast screening programme has not
OL,15,Fbeen amended - the age has not been
OL,16,Flowered since 1988 and we now know
OL,17,Fthat there are more women being
OL,18,Fdiagnosed earlier and later stage.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777061156
OL,3,CChemo nurse takes campaign to lower
OL,4,Cbreast cancer screening age to
OL,5,CWestminster
OL,7,F"As part of Wes Streeting's new cancer
OL,8,Ftarget plan, he emphasises the need
OL,9,Ffor earlier detection and as a cancer
OL,10,Fsurvivor himself, we need to stick
OL,11,Ftogether and we need to work to try
OL,12,Fand make a change for the people that
OL,13,Fwe love."
OL,15,FMore than 106,000 people have now
OL,16,Fsigned Gemma's petition calling for
OL,17,Fthe age limit to be lowered.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777061156
OL,3,CChemo nurse takes campaign to lower
OL,4,Cbreast cancer screening age to
OL,5,CWestminster
OL,7,FAs the petition has generated more
OL,8,Fthan 100,000 signatures, it means
OL,9,Fthere will be a debate in parliament
OL,10,Fover the next few months.
OL,12,FBut Gemma said despite securing a
OL,13,Fdebate, she doesn't want to lose
OL,14,Fmomentum.
OL,16,F"I don't want people thinking now
OL,17,Fthey've signed it, that's it like
OL,18,Fnothing else is happening and the more
OL,19,Fwe talk about it the more it is
OL,20,Fforgotten.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777061156
OL,3,CChemo nurse takes campaign to lower
OL,4,Cbreast cancer screening age to
OL,5,CWestminster
OL,7,F"We need to continue raising
OL,8,Fawareness."
OL,10,FThe Government says that in line with
OL,11,Findependent advice from the UK
OL,12,FNational Screening Committee, it does
OL,13,Fnot intend to lower the age or
OL,14,Fincrease the frequency of breast
OL,15,Fscreens.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
