OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777061156
OL,3,CChemo nurse takes campaign to lower
OL,4,Cbreast cancer screening age to
OL,5,CWestminster
OL,7,FIn a statement a spokesperson said
OL,8,F"Women younger than the age of 50 are
OL,9,Fnot routinely screened for breast
OL,10,Fcancer due to the lower risk of women
OL,11,Funder this age developing breast
OL,12,Fcancer, and the fact that women below
OL,13,F50 tend to have denser breasts.
OL,15,F"The denseness of breast tissue
OL,16,Freduces the ability of getting an
OL,17,Faccurate mammogram, the accepted
OL,18,Fscreening test for breast cancer.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777061156
OL,3,CChemo nurse takes campaign to lower
OL,4,Cbreast cancer screening age to
OL,5,CWestminster
OL,7,F"Due to this and other factors, there
OL,8,Fis a risk of over treatment and
OL,9,Fdistress for women who do not have
OL,10,Fbreast cancer but would be subjected
OL,11,Fto invasive and painful medical
OL,12,Ftreatments and diagnostic tests.
OL,14,F"The Marmot review found that
OL,15,Fscreening women outside the ages of 50-
OL,16,F70 could lead to over-diagnosis
OL,17,F(referring women for unnecessary
OL,18,Ftests) and over-treatment (operating
OL,19,Fon women with disease which is
OL,20,Funlikely to cause serious harm to
OL,21,Fthem)."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777061156
OL,3,CChemo nurse takes campaign to lower
OL,4,Cbreast cancer screening age to
OL,5,CWestminster
OL,7,FBut Gemma said as other countries take
OL,8,Fthe risk to screen from 40 then the UK
OL,9,Fshould follow suit.
OL,11,F"If it's a cost thing then obviously
OL,12,Fanything caught earlier is cost
OL,13,Feffective long term," Gemma added.
OL,15,F"If they spoke to people that have
OL,16,Fbeen diagnosed in their 40s, they
OL,17,Fwould be prepared to take that risk of
OL,18,Fbeing over diagnosed or not being
OL,19,Fdiagnosed at all."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777061156
OL,3,CChemo nurse takes campaign to lower
OL,4,Cbreast cancer screening age to
OL,5,CWestminster
OL,7,FThe Labour MP for East Thanet, Polly
OL,8,FBillington was at the protest.
OL,10,FShe told ITV Meridian: "I think people
OL,11,Flike Gemma who are absolutely on the
OL,12,Ffront line of our breast cancer care
OL,13,Fservices, if they start spotting
OL,14,Ftrends, I think it's worthwhile
OL,15,Fresponding to them.
OL,17,F"The clinical decisions that we've got
OL,18,Fare being made on evidence that may
OL,19,Fwell be a bit out of date.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777061156
OL,3,CChemo nurse takes campaign to lower
OL,4,Cbreast cancer screening age to
OL,5,CWestminster
OL,7,F"Review that evidence, see if it
OL,8,Freally is the best, and if mammograms
OL,9,Fare not the best way in order to test
OL,10,Ffor breast cancer at the age of 40, we
OL,11,Fshould be finding another way of doing
OL,12,Fit."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
