CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777061156
OL,3,CChemo nurse takes campaign to lower
OL,4,Cbreast cancer screening age to
OL,5,CWestminster
OL,7,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,8,Fspokesperson said: "We are taking
OL,9,Fdecisive action to tackle breast
OL,10,Fcancer head-on - including launching
OL,11,Fworld-leading AI trials to support
OL,12,Fanalysis of mammograms and driving
OL,13,Fforward vital research that improves
OL,14,Fcare and saves lives through our 10
OL,15,FYear Health Plan.
OL,26,@pD@TOU
