OL,3,CChemo nurse takes campaign to lower
OL,4,Cbreast cancer screening age to
OL,5,CWestminster
OL,7,F"Decisions regarding screening for
OL,8,Fbreast cancer are made based on the
OL,9,Fbest available evidence, with the
OL,10,Findependent UK National Screening
OL,11,FCommittee keeping all programmes under
OL,12,Fcareful review."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
